snippet.title: 5 True Crime Stories | Smartest Criminals in History Who Were Never Caught
snippet.description:
The true crime stories of the smartest criminals in the world will likely never be known. The smartest criminals don’t get caught. But sometimes they leave behind enough for us to know they know what they’re doing, even if their identity or location isn’t known.
